description:
Biography

Emily was born in Port Perry, Ontario. Her early career was noted for her role in primarily Canadian television and movies, but she has gradually become a recognizable face to the American market as well. Her most famous role to date is in the television series Revenge.

Comic Related Movie Roles

She plays Sharon Carter in the movie Captain America: The Winter Soldier.
name: Emily Van Camp
